{"tid":1154572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港做緊乜 深圳機場三跑擴建工程獲批 總投資93億","createTime":"2019-05-14T11:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T11:47:20.000Z","uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb324a3cabdd0c716b1da08035bd492fe4bb6cbf","tid":1154572,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"發改委公布，批覆深圳機場三跑道擴建工程，按照滿足2030年旅客輸送量8000萬人次、貨郵輸送量260萬噸的目標進行設計，項目總投資約93.5億元(人民幣‧下同)。<br />\n<br />\n公告稱，為適應航空業務量快速增長需要，提升機場綜合保障能力和服務水平，加快推進國際航空樞紐和珠三角地區世界級機場群建設，促進區域經濟社會發展，同意實施深圳機場三跑道擴建工程。<br />\n<br />\n項目總投資約93.5億元，其中，機場工程投資約88.6億元，由深圳市人民政府安排市本級財政公共預算解決；空管工程投資約4.9億元，由民航局安排民航發展基金解決。"},{"pid":"2ed81600cac101a23802e2a18e216d208ece6f74","tid":1154572,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2112119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2112119&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=51f21af4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2112119</a>"},{"pid":"1dadaebeaf435daeaf4c62dc1cabf7d013b337f2","tid":1154572,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:30:20.000Z","msg":"香港係幾倍"},{"pid":"944e750f9ceaeef7a08410f52a4f297016984637","tid":1154572,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:30:54.000Z","msg":"機管局高層肥洒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e357159dcd0b3f20329943c382c668dd74fbef","tid":1154572,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:31:08.000Z","msg":"不意外 咁唔滿意又唔去做野？"},{"pid":"cb1fa8d6876e335975f999012e32bede4867805c","tid":1154572,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"項目總投資約93.5億元，其中，機場工程投資約88.6億元，由深圳市人民政府安排市本級財政公共預算解決；<br />\n<br />\n<img s